names.fullName: Differential effect of YidC depletion on the membrane proteome of Escherichia coli under aerobic and anaerobic growth conditions.

attributeList.attribute: Price CE., Otto A., Fusetti F., Becher D., Hecker M., Driessen AJ.

UniProt entry A8A6G7, (strain HS) has been used for bait protein YidC/OxaA, as an entry for the strain used, SF100, is not available. (der Laan et al., EMBO 2001). All subsequent Uniprot entries have been mapped to reviewed (UniProtKB/Swiss-Prot)entries, where possible. No entry for the gene "rneE" (protein - Ribonuclease E), can be found, so the gene name "rne" has been used instead.
